show.title: Supreme Son-In-Law
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/pY7YtZ
show.description: Samay married into one of the country's most powerful families, only to be dismissed as a mere ghar jamaai—dependent and insignificant. But behind his quiet smile hid the Supreme Leader, a shadowy force controlling parliament, media, and money. As the elite scramble to protect their power, buried secrets erupt and alliances collapse. Samay's revenge unfolds silently, not through violence but with absolute dominance. In this ruthless game of kursi, love is leverage, loyalty is a lie, and the true king is the one no one saw coming.
